title: Movie Review ‘Unpregnant’: Abortion Information as Chick Flick | National Review
description: Veronica Clarke’s baby is the reason for the road trip, but the baby makes no appearance, and it is the child’s disappearance that renders the trip a success. Unpregnant claims to grapple with the abortion debate but settles for cheap smears and lazy slogans instead.
text: Movie Review ‘Unpregnant’: Abortion Information as Chick Flick | National Review
